# Things that would only land here by accident — extra safety belt.
# IDA db extensions are NOT excluded — the published implant_reconstructed.*
# files live under dump/. If you reanalyze your own targets locally,
# the resulting .id0/.id1/.i64 files are tracked too, so be deliberate
# about what you commit from any new analysis.
